#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.7:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Mettāvagga"
msgstr "1. Love"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Devadattavipattisutta"
msgstr "7. Devadatta’s Failure"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.7:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate acirapakkante "
"devadatte."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, on the Vulture’s Peak "
"Mountain, not long after Devadatta had left."

msgctxt "an8.7:1.2"
msgid "Tatra bhagavā devadattaṃ ārabbha bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There the Buddha spoke to the mendicants about Devadatta:"

msgctxt "an8.7:1.3"
msgid ""
"“sādhu, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kālena kālaṃ attavipattiṃ paccavekkhitā hoti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, it’s good for a mendicant to check their own failings from time "
"to time."

msgctxt "an8.7:1.4"
msgid "Sādhu, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kālena kālaṃ paravipattiṃ paccavekkhitā hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s good for a mendicant to check the failings of others from time to time."

msgctxt "an8.7:1.5"
msgid ""
"Sādhu, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kālena kālaṃ attasampattiṃ paccavekkhitā hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s good for a mendicant to check their own successes from time to time."

msgctxt "an8.7:1.6"
msgid ""
"Sādhu, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kālena kālaṃ parasampattiṃ paccavekkhitā hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s good for a mendicant to check the successes of others from time to time."

msgctxt "an8.7:1.7"
msgid ""
"Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, asaddhammehi abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto devadatto "
"āpāyiko nerayiko kappaṭṭho atekiccho."
msgstr ""
"Overcome and overwhelmed by eight things that oppose the true teaching, "
"Devadatta is going to a place of loss, to hell, there to remain for an eon, "
"irredeemable."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.7:2.1"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.7:2.2"
msgid ""
"Lābhena hi, bhikkhave, abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto devadatto āpāyiko nerayiko "
"kappaṭṭho atekiccho."
msgstr "Overcome and overwhelmed by gain …"

msgctxt "an8.7:2.3"
msgid "Alābhena, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr "loss …"

msgctxt "an8.7:2.4"
msgid "yasena, bhikkhave …"
msgstr "fame …"

msgctxt "an8.7:2.5"
msgid "ayasena, bhikkhave …"
msgstr "disgrace …"

msgctxt "an8.7:2.6"
msgid "sakkārena, bhikkhave …"
msgstr "honor …"

msgctxt "an8.7:2.7"
msgid "asakkārena, bhikkhave …"
msgstr "dishonor …"

msgctxt "an8.7:2.8"
msgid "pāpicchatāya, bhikkhave …"
msgstr "wicked desires …"

msgctxt "an8.7:2.9"
msgid ""
"pāpamittatāya, bhikkhave, abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto devadatto āpāyiko "
"nerayiko kappaṭṭho atekiccho."
msgstr ""
"bad friendship, Devadatta is going to a place of loss, to hell, there to "
"remain for an eon, irredeemable."

msgctxt "an8.7:2.10"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahi asaddhammehi abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto "
"devadatto āpāyiko nerayiko kappaṭṭho atekiccho."
msgstr ""
"Overcome and overwhelmed by these eight things that oppose the true "
"teaching, Devadatta is going to a place of loss, to hell, there to remain "
"for an eon, irredeemable."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli4.161"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.7:3.1"
msgid ""
"Sādhu, bhikkhave, bhikkhu uppannaṃ lābhaṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyya, "
msgstr ""
"It’s good for a mendicant, whenever they encounter it, to overcome gain … "

msgctxt "an8.7:3.2"
msgid "uppannaṃ alābhaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "loss …"

msgctxt "an8.7:3.3"
msgid "uppannaṃ yasaṃ …"
msgstr "fame …"

msgctxt "an8.7:3.4"
msgid "uppannaṃ ayasaṃ …"
msgstr "disgrace …"

msgctxt "an8.7:3.5"
msgid "uppannaṃ sakkāraṃ …"
msgstr "honor …"

msgctxt "an8.7:3.6"
msgid "uppannaṃ asakkāraṃ …"
msgstr "dishonor …"

msgctxt "an8.7:3.7"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpicchataṃ …"
msgstr "wicked desires …"

msgctxt "an8.7:3.8"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyya."
msgstr "bad friendship."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: Kiñca → kathañca (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an8.7:4.1"
msgid ""
"Kiñca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu atthavasaṃ paṭicca uppannaṃ lābhaṃ abhibhuyya "
"abhibhuyya vihareyya, "
msgstr "What advantage does a mendicant gain by overcoming these eight things?"

msgctxt "an8.7:4.2"
msgid "uppannaṃ alābhaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:4.3"
msgid "uppannaṃ yasaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:4.4"
msgid "uppannaṃ ayasaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:4.5"
msgid "uppannaṃ sakkāraṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:4.6"
msgid "uppannaṃ asakkāraṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:4.7"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpicchataṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:4.8"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyya?"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
#. VAR: uppannaṃ lābhaṃ anabhibhuyya → anabhibhuyya anabhibhuyya (mr)
#. VAR: lābhaṃ abhibhuyya → abhibhuyya abhibhuyya (mr)
msgctxt "an8.7:5.1"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ hissa, bhikkhave, uppannaṃ lābhaṃ anabhibhuyya viharato uppajjeyyuṃ "
"āsavā vighātapariḷāhā, uppannaṃ lābhaṃ abhibhuyya viharato evaṃsa te āsavā "
"vighātapariḷāhā na honti."
msgstr ""
"The distressing and feverish defilements that might arise in someone who "
"lives without overcoming these eight things do not arise when they have "
"overcome them."

msgctxt "an8.7:5.2"
msgid "Yaṃ hissa, bhikkhave, uppannaṃ alābhaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.3"
msgid "uppannaṃ yasaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.4"
msgid "uppannaṃ ayasaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.5"
msgid "uppannaṃ sakkāraṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.6"
msgid "uppannaṃ asakkāraṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.7"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpicchataṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.8"
msgid ""
"uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ anabhibhuyya viharato uppajjeyyuṃ āsavā "
"vighātapariḷāhā, uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ abhibhuyya viharato evaṃsa te āsavā "
"vighātapariḷāhā na honti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.9"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu atthavasaṃ paṭicca uppannaṃ lābhaṃ abhibhuyya "
"abhibhuyya vihareyya, "
msgstr ""
"This is the advantage that a mendicant gains by overcoming these eight "
"things."

msgctxt "an8.7:5.10"
msgid "uppannaṃ alābhaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.11"
msgid "uppannaṃ yasaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.12"
msgid "uppannaṃ ayasaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.13"
msgid "uppannaṃ sakkāraṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.14"
msgid "uppannaṃ asakkāraṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.15"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpicchataṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.7:5.16"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyya."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an8.7:6.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "So, mendicants, you should train like this:"

msgctxt "an8.7:6.2"
msgid "‘uppannaṃ lābhaṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya viharissāma, "
msgstr "‘Whenever we encounter it, we will overcome gain … "

msgctxt "an8.7:6.3"
msgid "uppannaṃ alābhaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "loss …"

msgctxt "an8.7:6.4"
msgid "uppannaṃ yasaṃ …"
msgstr "fame …"

msgctxt "an8.7:6.5"
msgid "uppannaṃ ayasaṃ …"
msgstr "disgrace …"

msgctxt "an8.7:6.6"
msgid "uppannaṃ sakkāraṃ …"
msgstr "honor …"

msgctxt "an8.7:6.7"
msgid "uppannaṃ asakkāraṃ …"
msgstr "dishonor …"

msgctxt "an8.7:6.8"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpicchataṃ …"
msgstr "wicked desires …"

msgctxt "an8.7:6.9"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya viharissāmā’ti."
msgstr "bad friendship.’"

msgctxt "an8.7:6.10"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr "That’s how you should train.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.7:6.11"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
